    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adult Egyptian patients

          -  18-60 years old

          -  Patients transplanted for HCV related disease and /or HCC

          -  Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Other etiologies for end stage liver disease (such as HBV and cholestatic liver
             disease and autoimmune hepatitis).
      </textblock>
